text: Mojtaba Zonnour (; also spelled Zolnour) is an Iranian Shi'a cleric and conservative politician. He represents Qom in the Iranian Parliament. Zonnour was formerly Supreme Leader's Deputy Representative to the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps. Zonnour was diagnosed with the SARS-CoV-2 in February 2020. ==References== Category:Iranian politicians Category:Living people Category:1963 births
title: Mojtaba Zonnour
